 constrain the parameters describing\nthe kinematical state of the Universe via a cosmographic approach at high\nredshifts (up to $z\\approx 10$), wherein we require a very minimal set of\nassumptions on the deep learning architecture itself that do not rely on\ndynamical equations for any specific theory of gravity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Sep 2021 22:12:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Mar 2022 23:48:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-20"}
