h the state-of-the-art methods, no matter\nin the general or cold-start scenario. And in the experiment of model variant\nanalysis, the benefits of the cross-channel matching representation model and\nthe hierarchical self-supervised model proposed in this paper are also fully\nverified.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Sep 2021 02:42:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Sep 2021 11:46:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 14 Sep 2021 02:20:53 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 11 Jun 2022 06:36:52 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 25 Sep 2022 02:39:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-27"}
