agnetization exhibits a\npseudo-gap behavior for low values of applied field. We also discuss the\ndependence of NMR spectrum on various XXZ impurities and identify that the spin\nstate of Co impurity in SrCu$_{0.99}$Co$_{0.01}$O$_2$ is $S = 3/2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Sep 2021 08:19:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-15"}
