 top-down or a bottom-up approach are the most\ndeterminant factors in the regionalization process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Sep 2021 14:06:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Mar 2022 13:32:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-06"}
